The construction of the hostel in Ratnagiri
Department of Social Justice and Special Assistance
Government Memorandum No: BCH-2025 / Q.92 / Constructions
Madam Kama Marg, Martyr Rajguru Chowk,
Reference: - Department of Social Justice and Special Assistance, Government Decision No. BCH-2025 / Q. 124 / Constructions,

Dr. Babasaheb Ambedkar Government Hostel for Backward Class Children, Jail Road, Ratnagiri District under Social Justice and Special Assistance Department has been constructed at a cost of Rs. 13.53 Rs. / - Government Decisions referring to the construction budget. Administrative approval has been granted subject to the ACPA prescribed under 01.07.2025; the Government Decision includes condition number (s) as follows: -
The operational mechanism for the present construction will be Maharashtra-State Infrastructure Development Corporation (MSIDC), Mumbai.
(2) The other provisions of the Government Decision shall remain in force.
